iteditedit brings your emacs-snapshot (v23) python ide
The intention of this configuration is to provide the smoothest python programming possible with one of the most powerfull editors on the planet.

Things to do before your up and running.

Comes precompiled with Cedet 1.0pre6.

Install rope, ropemacs, ropemode:
hg clone http://bitbucket.org/agr/rope
hg clone http://bitbucket.org/agr/ropemacs
hg clone http://bitbucket.org/agr/ropemode

Install pymacs:
http://pymacs.progiciels-bpi.ca/archives/Pymacs.tar.gz

Install yasnippet (v.53 tested and works):
http://yasnippet.googlecode.com/files/yasnippet-0.5.3.tar.bz2
